霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone) 解释了为什么匆忙推出新专辑没有成功https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-explains-why-rushing-her-upcoming-album-didnt-work-3478979?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=holly-humberstone-explains-why-赶着她即将发行的专辑没有成功Anagricel DuranSun, 06 Aug 2023 22:41:20 +0000 LollapaloozaMusic InterviewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3478979 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone) 将于 2023 年 8 月 4 日在魁北克省蒙特利尔的 Parc Jean-Drapeau 举办的 Osheaga 音乐艺术节上表演。图片来源：马克·霍顿/盖蒂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我确实尝试着急于写东西，但并没有真正发挥作用”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-explains-why-rushing-her-upcoming-album-didnt-work-3478979">霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone) 的帖子解释了为什么催促她即将发行的专辑不起作用，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone) 将于 2023 年 8 月 4 日在魁北克省蒙特利尔的 Parc Jean-Drapeau 举办的 Osheaga 音乐艺术节上表演。图片来源：马克·霍顿/盖蒂" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/holly-humberstone">霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone)</a>解释了为什么在即将推出的首张专辑中仓促创作对她来说并不奏效。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/karol-g-live-at-lollapalooza-the-history-maker-transforms-the-fest-into-a-backyard-summer-party-3478348">Karol G 在 2023 年 Lollapalooza 现场演出：这位历史创造者将盛宴转变为后院夏日派对</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/lollapalooza">2023 年 Lollapalooza</a>演出前，亨伯斯通在后台接受<em>NME</em>采访时，谈到了她即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-announces-debut-album-paint-my-bedroom-black-3462992">Paint My Bedroom Black</a> 》及其背后的创作过程。</p><p> “我确实试图匆忙写一些东西，但它并没有真正起作用，”这位歌手解释道。 “我的音乐对我来说一直都是非常个人化的，走进录音室并写下正在发生的事情对我的心理健康来说总是非常重要的，所以我发现这是慢慢来的过程的一部分。如果我尝试的话，我不可能做得更快。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我希望这是我迄今为止做过的最喜欢的事情。我觉得对于很多我最喜欢的艺术家来说，他们的首张专辑一直是最具标志性的作品，所以我希望它能代表我的“T”，我希望它感觉它真的来自我的内心，听起来真的很令人畏惧，但我做到了。只是我觉得你不能着急。” </p><figure id="attachment_3463014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3463014" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3463014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot.jpg" alt="霍莉·亨伯斯通。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Press-Shot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3463014" class="wp-caption-text">霍莉·亨伯斯通。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>亨伯斯通还表示，她在巡演中创作大部分唱片时，探索了歌曲创作中以前从未探索过的新领域。</p><p> “我觉得去年我感受到了以前从未真正经历过的事情，因为这对我来说仍然很新鲜。我发现我自己有两个不同的一面，所以这张专辑被分成两半，一半是我的外向部分，我知道我已经在那里，而另一半则更黑暗，有点想要将世界拒之门外。我猜是我，我也参与其中，”她说。</p><p>她补充道：“它的标题是‘把我的房间漆成黑色’，因为我觉得这概括了一切。它比我以前写过的任何东西都更加个人化，我对此感到非常自豪。我有点害怕发布它，只是因为我非常关心它，所以我想这是一件好事。”</p><p>在其他地方，Humberstone 分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-shares-what-it-was-like-working-with-d4vid-at-lollapalooza-20203-3478965">与 D4vd 合作制作她的单曲“Superbloodmoon”的</a>感受。 </p><figure id="attachment_3463009" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3463009" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3463009" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork.jpg" alt="霍莉·亨伯斯通“Paint My Room Black”专辑封面。图片来源：康斯坦丁/斯宾塞" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Holly-Humberstone-Paint-My-Room-Black-album-artwork-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3463009" class="wp-caption-text">霍莉·亨伯斯通“Paint My Room Black”专辑封面。图片来源：康斯坦丁/斯宾塞</figcaption></figure><p>“与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d4vd">D4vd</a>合作真是太酷了。自从他开始发行音乐以来，我一直是他的粉丝。他在英国巡演，我问他是否愿意进入工作室，我们就写了《超级血月》。”</p><p> Humberstone 的首张专辑《Paint My Room Black》将于 10 月 19 日通过 Polydor/Darkroom/Geffen 发行。<a href="https://hh.lnk.to/PaintMyBedroomBlackWe">请访问此处</a>预订 LP。</p><p>整个周末<i>请回来 NME，</i>了解有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lollapalooza"><i>Lollapalooza 2023</i></a><i>的更多评论、新闻、采访、照片等</i><i>。</i></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-explains-why-rushing-her-upcoming-album-didnt-work-3478979">霍莉·亨伯斯通 (Holly Humberstone) 的帖子解释了为什么催促她即将发行的专辑不起作用，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
